1
00:01:00,100 --> 00:01:02,900
=Daughter of Fortune=

2
00:01:02,900 --> 00:01:05,460
(Adapted from the novel
"Phoenix Palace Dream" by Lan Jiujiu)

3
00:01:05,540 --> 00:01:08,460
=Episode 19=

4
00:01:09,840 --> 00:01:11,799
Anyway, you should be punished too.

5
00:01:12,319 --> 00:01:13,599
Someone was badmouthing me,

6
00:01:13,650 --> 00:01:14,900
and you didn't speak up for me.

7
00:01:15,159 --> 00:01:16,920
How would I dare interrupt?

8
00:01:25,599 --> 00:01:26,879
You just enjoy

9
00:01:27,159 --> 00:01:28,640
watching people scold me.

10
00:01:29,439 --> 00:01:32,719
(Nangong Xuanyu has become so childish.)

11
00:01:33,560 --> 00:01:34,719
Want to see

12
00:01:34,879 --> 00:01:36,480
the most charming man in Daliang cook?

13
00:01:38,920 --> 00:01:40,079
Your Majesty.

14
00:01:56,200 --> 00:01:58,719
I never expected the noble Lord Jiang

15
00:01:58,920 --> 00:02:00,239
to know how to cook.

16
00:02:00,480 --> 00:02:01,599
My tastes are rather light.

17
00:02:01,610 --> 00:02:03,200
I'm not used to food prepared by others.

18
00:02:05,200 --> 00:02:07,879
Lord Jiang, you have
a full collection of spices.

19
00:02:08,170 --> 00:02:09,700
He has a particular fondness for them.

20
00:02:10,000 --> 00:02:11,039
He knows

21
00:02:11,240 --> 00:02:12,599
all kinds of spices.

22
00:02:14,680 --> 00:02:15,879
But they all

23
00:02:15,879 --> 00:02:17,240
look pretty similar.

24
00:02:17,560 --> 00:02:18,680
They're different.

25
00:02:20,560 --> 00:02:22,000
Each blend

26
00:02:22,319 --> 00:02:23,719
brings out a different fragrance.

27
00:02:24,680 --> 00:02:27,759
I never knew you knew spices so well.

28
00:02:29,240 --> 00:02:30,410
I learned it from Madam Lian,

29
00:02:30,560 --> 00:02:32,560
who served beside His Majesty's mother.

30
00:02:33,380 --> 00:02:35,319
She was especially skilled
at making fish congee.

31
00:02:39,800 --> 00:02:41,080
It's a pity...

32
00:02:41,719 --> 00:02:43,800
When I went to collect her body,

33
00:02:44,800 --> 00:02:46,199
there was a basket beside her.

34
00:02:48,400 --> 00:02:49,199
Inside the basket,

35
00:02:49,520 --> 00:02:50,719
there was a Peng fish.

36
00:02:55,159 --> 00:02:56,680
Let's not bring up sad things.

37
00:02:57,520 --> 00:02:57,879
Come.

38
00:02:58,039 --> 00:02:59,120
Try the congee.

39
00:03:17,039 --> 00:03:17,680
Have a taste

40
00:03:18,080 --> 00:03:19,719
of the fish congee

41
00:03:20,039 --> 00:03:21,680
made by Daliang's most charming man.

42
00:03:31,639 --> 00:03:33,400
Must you mock me like this?

43
00:03:34,240 --> 00:03:36,520
Those were Lady Shen's exact words.

44
00:03:37,800 --> 00:03:40,000
Also, stones like jade
lay heaped together,

45
00:03:40,010 --> 00:03:41,690
and verdant pines stood in rows
like emeralds.

46
00:03:45,680 --> 00:03:46,840
I'm sorry.

47
00:03:47,000 --> 00:03:48,000
Please stop.

48
00:03:48,240 --> 00:03:49,680
So you do know when you're wrong?

49
00:04:07,520 --> 00:04:08,319
Your Majesty!

50
00:04:08,390 --> 00:04:08,960
Your Majesty!

51
00:04:09,400 --> 00:04:10,080
Your Majesty!

52
00:04:14,919 --> 00:04:16,580
Your Majesty, let's return to the palace.

53
00:04:20,959 --> 00:04:21,439
Come.

54
00:04:38,120 --> 00:04:40,000
The Prince of Jin was right.

55
00:04:40,000 --> 00:04:41,260
The moment the white flute was played,

56
00:04:41,279 --> 00:04:42,290
he immediately coughed up.

57
00:04:45,000 --> 00:04:47,120
When Nangong Xuanyu
was exiled to the imperial temple,

58
00:04:47,319 --> 00:04:49,160
the late emperor forced poison into him.

59
00:04:49,399 --> 00:04:51,000
It flares up every full moon,

60
00:04:51,199 --> 00:04:53,240
causing unbearable agony.

61
00:04:53,759 --> 00:04:54,639
In recent years,

62
00:04:55,000 --> 00:04:56,680
he has kept a white snake by his side.

63
00:04:57,199 --> 00:04:57,959
That snake

64
00:04:58,160 --> 00:04:59,439
is used to suppress the poison.

65
00:05:00,680 --> 00:05:02,360
How did the Prince of Jin

66
00:05:02,519 --> 00:05:03,480
come to know

67
00:05:03,480 --> 00:05:05,720
such a secret about him?

68
00:05:08,040 --> 00:05:09,160
This man is dangerous.

69
00:05:09,160 --> 00:05:09,839
Your Lordship,

70
00:05:10,040 --> 00:05:11,079
we'd best be cautious.

71
00:05:12,399 --> 00:05:14,160
This is Daliang's capital.

72
00:05:14,480 --> 00:05:16,319
Does he think he can rival me?

73
00:05:16,720 --> 00:05:17,319
Father.

74
00:05:28,060 --> 00:05:29,759
What have you done
to His Majesty, Father?

75
00:05:30,680 --> 00:05:32,120
What are you talking about?

76
00:05:32,250 --> 00:05:33,519
What could I possibly have done?

77
00:05:34,079 --> 00:05:35,800
You're a minister of Daliang.

78
00:05:36,360 --> 00:05:38,199
You should serve His Majesty with loyalty.

79
00:05:40,360 --> 00:05:41,560
Go back.

80
00:05:42,519 --> 00:05:45,759
I ask nothing of you
for the sake of the Jiang family.

81
00:05:46,240 --> 00:05:48,600
Simply live out your days
as a carefree nobleman.

82
00:05:49,070 --> 00:05:50,920
Daliang has suffered
through years of turmoil.

83
00:05:51,199 --> 00:05:52,439
The people have only recently

84
00:05:52,439 --> 00:05:53,680
regained peace and stability.

85
00:05:54,550 --> 00:05:56,079
I hope you won't stir up more trouble.

86
00:05:59,279 --> 00:06:00,079
Leave.

87
00:06:00,480 --> 00:06:02,000
Useless trash.

88
00:06:04,120 --> 00:06:04,920
Yes.

89
00:06:12,079 --> 00:06:13,040
Young Master is kind

90
00:06:13,040 --> 00:06:13,879
and loyal.

91
00:06:14,160 --> 00:06:16,439
He must've been bewitched
by Nangong Xuanyu.

92
00:06:16,439 --> 00:06:18,199
That's why he spoke out of turn.

93
00:06:18,519 --> 00:06:19,920
If I had known,

94
00:06:20,399 --> 00:06:21,680
I never would've let him befriend

95
00:06:21,680 --> 00:06:23,399
Nangong Xuanyu.

96
00:06:24,120 --> 00:06:26,780
(The one controlling the game
must never act rashly or impatiently.)

97
00:06:27,959 --> 00:06:29,680
(Father misplayed his hand this time.)

98
00:06:30,199 --> 00:06:32,399
What will we do next, Young Master?

99
00:06:33,079 --> 00:06:34,000
Wait.

100
00:06:37,399 --> 00:06:38,720
Are you really fine?

101
00:06:38,959 --> 00:06:40,600
Shouldn't we visit
the Imperial Hospital?

102
00:06:41,040 --> 00:06:43,519
It was only a rush of blood
this morning.

103
00:06:44,560 --> 00:06:46,240
I'm fine now.

104
00:06:48,160 --> 00:06:49,199
I should get going.

105
00:06:49,399 --> 00:06:50,800
I'll come tomorrow night.

106
00:06:54,040 --> 00:06:55,260
I bid farewell to Your Majesty.

107
00:06:57,079 --> 00:06:59,240
Young Lady, the escort agency
just sent word.

108
00:06:59,560 --> 00:07:01,040
After the gold token left the palace,

109
00:07:01,040 --> 00:07:01,759
it disappeared.

110
00:07:02,000 --> 00:07:02,800
What?

111
00:07:04,560 --> 00:07:05,480
I'll go see His Majesty

112
00:07:05,600 --> 00:07:07,000
and find a way to reclaim it.

113
00:07:13,639 --> 00:07:14,399
Your...

114
00:07:18,660 --> 00:07:19,180
(Cold Palace)

115
00:07:20,040 --> 00:07:21,820
Why would His Majesty
go to the Cold Palace?

116
00:08:11,240 --> 00:08:12,879
There's a secret chamber here.

117
00:08:13,319 --> 00:08:15,120
That explains why he appeared here

118
00:08:16,079 --> 00:08:17,639
the first time I met him.

119
00:08:35,600 --> 00:08:36,600
We haven't found

120
00:08:36,670 --> 00:08:38,440
Lady Shen's maternal family
at Mount Nanhua.

121
00:08:39,200 --> 00:08:41,240
How should we report this to His Majesty?

122
00:08:41,450 --> 00:08:44,110
It's more a matter of how His Majesty
will explain it to Lady Shen.

123
00:08:45,200 --> 00:08:46,360
This is bad.

124
00:08:46,700 --> 00:08:48,399
We secretly brought them
into the capital,

125
00:08:48,399 --> 00:08:49,360
and now we've lost them.

126
00:08:50,360 --> 00:08:52,360
Send more men to continue the search.

127
00:08:53,080 --> 00:08:53,759
Yes.

128
00:09:02,879 --> 00:09:04,600
(He captured my mother's family.)

129
00:09:05,200 --> 00:09:06,519
(What is he trying to do?)

130
00:09:07,240 --> 00:09:07,879
Your Majesty,

131
00:09:08,000 --> 00:09:09,960
our men haven't found
Lady Shen's maternal relatives

132
00:09:10,120 --> 00:09:11,080
at Mount Nanhua.

133
00:09:11,840 --> 00:09:13,039
Send more men.

134
00:09:13,360 --> 00:09:14,399
We're short-handed.

135
00:09:15,120 --> 00:09:15,919
Duke Zhen's forces

136
00:09:15,919 --> 00:09:17,559
are quietly advancing
toward the capital.

137
00:09:18,000 --> 00:09:19,519
Your Majesty also needs more men.

138
00:09:19,879 --> 00:09:21,639
Duke Zhen won't start a war so easily.

139
00:09:22,519 --> 00:09:24,039
His troop has fought too many battles.

140
00:09:24,380 --> 00:09:25,840
All they want now is a peaceful life.

141
00:09:26,639 --> 00:09:27,840
Keep them occupied for now.

142
00:09:28,360 --> 00:09:30,560
The matter at Mount Nanhua
can't be delayed any longer.

143
00:09:30,919 --> 00:09:31,679
Yes.

144
00:09:32,600 --> 00:09:33,720
Right. Tomorrow night,

145
00:09:34,100 --> 00:09:36,200
I want to make up a proper wedding night
for Zhinian.

146
00:09:36,960 --> 00:09:38,039
Have Eunuch Ming

147
00:09:38,159 --> 00:09:39,399
prepare my chamber.

148
00:09:40,399 --> 00:09:40,840
Understood.

149
00:09:41,000 --> 00:09:42,190
Congratulations, Your Majesty.

150
00:09:42,320 --> 00:09:43,399
May you and Lady Shen

151
00:09:43,400 --> 00:09:45,320
share a lifetime of love
and grow old together.

152
00:09:45,600 --> 00:09:46,960
Smooth talker.

153
00:09:47,440 --> 00:09:48,399
What reward do you want?

154
00:09:48,639 --> 00:09:49,279
Help yourself.

155
00:09:49,399 --> 00:09:49,879
Sure.

156
00:09:50,320 --> 00:09:51,360
I won't hold back then.

157
00:09:51,840 --> 00:09:52,799
Take your reward,

158
00:09:53,080 --> 00:09:54,000
then go do your job.

159
00:09:54,100 --> 00:09:56,120
Also, the Prince of Jin
has snuck into the capital

160
00:09:56,130 --> 00:09:57,020
and is showing himself everywhere.

161
00:09:57,039 --> 00:09:58,200
He must have some purpose.

162
00:09:58,840 --> 00:09:59,799
Find out what it is.

163
00:10:00,080 --> 00:10:00,679
Understood.

164
00:10:47,279 --> 00:10:51,360
(This is Nangong Xuanyu's
secret chamber?)

165
00:11:18,559 --> 00:11:20,320
Shen Zhinian, 19 years old.

166
00:11:20,639 --> 00:11:23,600
Her father is Shen Maoxue,
a finance officer of Chizhou Prefecture.

167
00:11:23,919 --> 00:11:25,039
Born to a concubine.

168
00:11:25,240 --> 00:11:26,220
Lost her mother at seven

169
00:11:26,230 --> 00:11:27,790
and was raised under Madam Shen's care.

170
00:11:29,559 --> 00:11:30,679
(This is...)

171
00:11:31,679 --> 00:11:33,399
(He has been investigating me
all along.)

172
00:11:34,159 --> 00:11:36,480
(He recorded every word I said)

173
00:11:36,879 --> 00:11:38,440
(and everything I did.)

174
00:11:39,000 --> 00:11:40,559
Madam Shen refused to let her mother

175
00:11:40,559 --> 00:11:41,940
be buried in the Shen family tombs.

176
00:11:42,720 --> 00:11:43,960
She carried the memorial tablet

177
00:11:44,360 --> 00:11:46,159
and chased after her mother's coffin

178
00:11:47,080 --> 00:11:49,360
through the snow
for two days and two nights.

179
00:11:50,519 --> 00:11:51,759
(What am I)

180
00:11:52,000 --> 00:11:53,679
(to him?)

181
00:11:54,559 --> 00:11:57,120
(Were all those feelings he showed me
just an act?)

182
00:11:57,919 --> 00:11:59,440
(Nangong Xuanyu,)

183
00:11:59,720 --> 00:12:01,480
(you're better at pretending than I am.)

184
00:12:12,580 --> 00:12:14,140
(Death-exemption Medal)

185
00:12:14,140 --> 00:12:16,500
♪If we don't meet♪

186
00:12:16,500 --> 00:12:20,100
♪Flowers bloom and fall in shame♪

187
00:12:22,600 --> 00:12:25,000
He's been acting in front of me
the whole time.

188
00:12:27,360 --> 00:12:33,800
♪Spring breeze passes,
dancing through the years♪

189
00:12:34,160 --> 00:12:40,480
♪Brewing longing,
remembering past lives♪

190
00:12:41,000 --> 00:12:47,680
♪Hard to meet, and just as hard to part♪

191
00:12:47,680 --> 00:12:54,560
♪Who planted the beans
that grew into lotuses?♪

192
00:12:54,800 --> 00:13:00,680
♪Spring breeze passes,
composing the fleeting years♪

193
00:13:01,600 --> 00:13:08,200
♪Clouds on Mount Wu,
no sails on the sea♪

194
00:13:08,360 --> 00:13:15,040
♪Wanting to fold my heart
into a paper kite♪

195
00:13:15,320 --> 00:13:21,760
♪But the ties are too tangled to sever♪

196
00:13:36,660 --> 00:13:41,820
♪Broken dreams,
listening to the light rain♪

197
00:13:43,380 --> 00:13:48,620
♪Bitter cold, bringing mist to the eyes♪

198
00:13:50,100 --> 00:13:52,580
♪If we don't meet♪

199
00:13:52,580 --> 00:13:56,140
♪Flowers bloom and fall in shame♪

200
00:13:56,180 --> 00:14:02,980
♪If we meet again,
the peaches will be warm♪

201
00:14:02,980 --> 00:14:08,460
♪Spring breeze passes,
dancing through the years♪

